nodes.text: Sata Neek was an Ishi Tib male who served in the New Republic's Riot Squadron. Neek fought in the Battle of Endor and continued to serve in Riot Squadron until the Attack on the Hellion's Dare, where he was killed by pilots of the 204th Imperial Fighter Wing.
Sata Neek was a dramatic storyteller despite many of his stories being false or made up. He was prone to boasting about his piloting skills and exaggerating stories and his own abilities.
